      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's the Apex Titan-X series. we're looking at the pro package. i saw the marketing materials saying \"unmatched endurance for continuous operation.\" our worksite is remote so if it dies halfway through the shift, it's a huge problem for us. i just need a straight answer on the 24-hour thing.",
