      "role": "user",
      "content": "look, i get the \"depends on load\" disclaimer, but the brochures specifically tout the 24-hour continuous use capability for the Titan-X. we have a huge contract to fulfill and if your product can't actually do what the marketing says, we can't move forward. are you saying the 24-hour claim in your own materials is misleading, or is it actually capable of hitting that mark for a standard heavy-duty shift?",
