      "content": "I understand your need for certainty, and our marketing materials are based on rigorous testing under specified load profiles. When we state 24-hour continuous operation, it generally refers to sustained, heavy-duty operation *within* the parameters tested, not necessarily at maximum sustained strain for the entire period. For mission-critical applications like yours, I suggest discussing a specialized, high-capacity battery rental or external power solution alongside the drill to absolutely guarantee uptime.",
